Ballina &amp; Byron Shire Residents devastated by flooding (and Residents from other neighbouring areas) are just as deserving of help as Lismore residents. @JElliotMP 

@ScottMorrisonMP - Why isn’t my friend eligible for help???

 #Floods2022 #NationalEmergency

@only2beyourself @PMGPSC @VSTMMJJ If a person can't live in the property, why on earth would they be expected to pay rent?
It makes no sense.
Surely, somewhere there's something about a place having to be fit for human habitation if you want to charge people for it.
